{"tid":1957491,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[引用] 香港特首人工每日高達$14274","createTime":"2020-04-04T03:31:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T06:38:45.000Z","uid":149188,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b30d4cd20fa4e9235877e10af4e66673ebb55aef","tid":1957491,"uid":149188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T03:31:12.000Z","msg":"疫情下百業蕭條，打工仔隨時飯碗不保，特首林鄭今年年薪卻繼續加，特首辦回覆查詢指林鄭年薪為521萬元，即月薪43萬，另外非實報實銷酬酢津貼為 98.2 萬元。<br />\n<br />\n根據美國財經網站「24/7 Wall S」於2019年的統計，全球年薪最高的10名領導人為：<br />\n<br />\n1. 新加坡總理李顯龍－1255萬港元<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. 香港特首林鄭月娥－509萬港元</span></strong><br />\n3. 前瑞士聯邦總統毛雷爾－376萬港元<br />\n4. 美國總統特朗普－311萬港元<br />\n5. 澳洲總理莫里森－294萬港元<br />\n6. 德國總理默克爾－287萬港元<br />\n7.  紐西蘭總理阿爾登－264萬港元<br />\n8. 前茅利塔尼亞總統阿齊茲－257萬港元<br />\n9. 奧地利總理古斯－256萬港元<br />\n10. 盧林堡首相貝特爾－216萬港元<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">全球第二高</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>達HKD$14274一日</ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n參考資料：<br />\n《20 Highest Paid World Leaders》<br />\n<a href=\"https://247wallst.com/special-report/2019/04/16/20-highest-paid-world-leaders-3/5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F247wallst.com%2Fspecial-report%2F2019%2F04%2F16%2F20-highest-paid-world-leaders-3%2F5%2F&d=dfx5yx0%2Fy135WOof7TdQyilkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=0df924da\" target=\"_blank\">https://247wallst.com/special-report/2019/04/16/20-highest-paid-world-leaders-3/5/</a><br />\n_________<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dgtwAqH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdgtwAqH.jpg&h=2fc2f747&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n出處 : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/116918276356673/posts/231416994906800/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F116918276356673%2Fposts%2F231416994906800%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=dfx5yx0%2Fy135WOof7TdQyilkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=8356e143\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/116918276356673/posts/231416994906800/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"5c13be85e19ed235aaa89ecc5d1ddec47d0b2f31","tid":1957491,"uid":149188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T03:32:56.000Z","msg":"Push 1/5"},{"pid":"51c69a158cd42090f3c2cd1ee5cba0cb99503adf","tid":1957491,"uid":149188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T03:33:47.000Z","msg":"2/5"},{"pid":"131d459755e1504de37b34e4523b3fcaae0780a6","tid":1957491,"uid":149188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T03:34:07.000Z","msg":"3/5"},{"pid":"5a3ea32aea3673f0100fad4d29ddb40775a9526a","tid":1957491,"uid":149188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T03:34:42.000Z","msg":"4/5"},{"pid":"555da6c07e61c96a8c0bdd64520a46475e8d56a0","tid":1957491,"uid":149188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T03:35:23.000Z","msg":"5/5"},{"pid":"849fdd655a9cc3c827068de64aada9c38cdca079","tid":1957491,"uid":126621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T03:40:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 政府財赤</span></strong></span><br />\n減人工好合理姐<br />\n政府收支唔平衡唔通加人工？<br />\n成班都唔用腦<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2.政府人工同私人市場無直接關係</span></span></strong><br />\n間公司賺定蝕先係最直接關係<br />\n唔好再打飛機話政府減薪<br />\n出面就減好撚多呢d 廢話<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">政府減唔減 出面已經減左</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3.係政府限制左黑警同公務員同一個pool</span></span></strong><br />\n要加一齊加 要減一齊減<br />\n請矛頭直指捆綁式機制<br />\n而且係黑警搞到政府財赤<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">4.減左50%=可請多一倍公務員</span></strong></span><br />\n減低失業率（多左17萬人就業）"},{"pid":"ef6b16675f124dfc1caf478d94c6cd46a32ef326","tid":1957491,"uid":149188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite